WEBVTT

00:01:03.670 --> 00:01:04.670
Three on the left.

00:01:06.430 --> 00:01:07.290
One at the back.

00:01:19.039 --> 00:01:19.970
Two at the front.

00:01:24.870 --> 00:01:26.670
Four on the left. Six at the back.

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:33.460
Five at the back. One at the front.

00:02:25.320 --> 00:02:26.400
Kill him.

00:02:26.970 --> 00:02:28.020
Kill him!

00:02:29.110 --> 00:02:30.140
Kill him!

00:02:30.950 --> 00:02:32.340
Kill him!

00:02:32.910 --> 00:02:33.810
Are you crazy?

00:02:34.410 --> 00:02:35.350
Are you crazy?

00:02:41.640 --> 00:02:42.510
Shrimpie!

00:04:17.769 --> 00:04:24.230
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

00:04:24.610 --> 00:04:27.100
[Episode 19]

00:04:51.060 --> 00:04:51.860
Maniacs!

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:54.220
Both of them are crazy.

00:04:58.750 --> 00:04:59.960
Which way did they go?

00:05:00.820 --> 00:05:02.030
Which way did they go?

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:03.870
They...

00:05:05.100 --> 00:05:06.040
I heard...

00:05:07.240 --> 00:05:08.700
They ran outside.

00:05:11.980 --> 00:05:13.580
Everyone who can still move,

00:05:14.270 --> 00:05:15.930
Come with me to chase them now!

00:05:58.920 --> 00:05:59.830
I heard...

00:06:00.690 --> 00:06:02.190
They ran outside.

00:06:06.410 --> 00:06:07.280
It's a trap.

00:06:39.810 --> 00:06:41.340
Let's take a breather here.

00:06:41.370 --> 00:06:43.030
They won't catch up that fast.

00:06:47.720 --> 00:06:49.050
Are you out of your mind?

00:06:49.510 --> 00:06:51.100
What were you doing, Zhang Haixia?

00:06:51.100 --> 00:06:53.100
You've never been like that before.

00:06:54.930 --> 00:06:56.730
Was it because of that medicine?

00:07:06.050 --> 00:07:07.650
What was so strange about it?

00:07:11.710 --> 00:07:12.710
Your expression.

00:07:19.530 --> 00:07:20.990
What about my expression?

00:07:22.490 --> 00:07:24.690
An expression you had never had before.

00:07:30.630 --> 00:07:32.490
I'd like to know what you're up to.

00:07:33.060 --> 00:07:33.740
What?

00:07:34.300 --> 00:07:35.690
You went to the Archives,

00:07:35.690 --> 00:07:36.890
Became a member of the Zhang family,

00:07:36.890 --> 00:07:39.020
And now you think you know everything?

00:07:39.750 --> 00:07:40.510
Don't be ridiculous.

00:07:40.510 --> 00:07:41.310
Zhang Haixia!

00:07:42.330 --> 00:07:43.570
Who possessed you?

00:07:47.810 --> 00:07:49.270
Are you even Zhang Haixia?

00:07:51.170 --> 00:07:52.430
What's wrong with you?

00:07:53.000 --> 00:07:54.530
Of course I am Zhang Haixia.

00:07:54.860 --> 00:07:56.190
And I'm perfectly fine.

00:07:58.760 --> 00:08:00.560
I feel better than ever.

00:08:02.590 --> 00:08:04.790
Then what about the injury on your hand?

00:08:04.860 --> 00:08:05.990
You're so annoying.

00:08:10.980 --> 00:08:12.640
I had planned everything out.

00:08:13.190 --> 00:08:14.390
I wasn't going to die.

00:08:15.420 --> 00:08:17.180
And even if that person had died,

00:08:17.180 --> 00:08:19.980
Zhang Qishan would definitely make the next move.

00:08:20.050 --> 00:08:22.180
Isn't this the way you liked it before?

00:08:22.560 --> 00:08:24.160
Did I restrict you too much

00:08:24.770 --> 00:08:26.370
And make you so overcautious

00:08:27.250 --> 00:08:28.140
That even such a small matter

00:08:28.140 --> 00:08:29.390
Made you so nervous?

00:08:43.770 --> 00:08:44.340
Fine.

00:08:45.500 --> 00:08:46.250
I got it.

00:08:46.910 --> 00:08:47.720
But for future operations,

00:08:47.720 --> 00:08:49.320
We must stay together, okay?

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:16.780
Don't move!

00:09:24.210 --> 00:09:24.930
Over there!

00:09:31.260 --> 00:09:32.520
He's there! After him!

00:09:41.410 --> 00:09:43.140
Did you see a man with a cripple?

00:09:45.530 --> 00:09:46.460
Where were they?

00:09:53.210 --> 00:09:53.740
Let's go!

00:09:58.500 --> 00:09:59.320
Sir,

00:09:59.700 --> 00:10:00.960
There are a lot of bugs here.

00:10:00.960 --> 00:10:02.560
Would you like to sit inside?

00:10:28.430 --> 00:10:31.870
[Ninth Master Xie, the Ninth Clan of the Old Nine Clans]

00:10:39.630 --> 00:10:41.030
Do you know how to play Go?

00:10:42.940 --> 00:10:43.670
A little bit.

00:11:13.470 --> 00:11:14.930
You call this a little bit?

00:11:23.990 --> 00:11:26.540
[Shun's Grocery Store]

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:53.960
[Heibei the Sixth, the Sixth Clan of the Old Nine Clans]

00:12:31.220 --> 00:12:33.580
Are all you Changxiang people so hot-tempered?

00:12:33.580 --> 00:12:35.030
It's from eating spicy food?

00:12:35.030 --> 00:12:36.490
I was entrusted by someone

00:12:36.580 --> 00:12:37.910
To block your way today.

00:12:38.100 --> 00:12:39.130
If you beat me,

00:12:39.290 --> 00:12:40.020
You can pass.

00:12:40.940 --> 00:12:41.820
If you can't,

00:12:42.370 --> 00:12:43.630
Get out of Changxiang.

00:13:49.550 --> 00:13:50.840
I haven't asked you yet.

00:13:50.840 --> 00:13:51.500
Sir.

00:13:52.580 --> 00:13:53.910
Who exactly are you?

00:13:59.620 --> 00:14:01.080
Did Zhang Qishan send you?

00:14:01.150 --> 00:14:01.940
How much is he paying?

00:14:01.940 --> 00:14:02.870
I'll pay triple.

00:14:02.980 --> 00:14:03.620
Take me to him.

00:14:03.620 --> 00:14:05.020
This is just the deposit.

00:14:06.240 --> 00:14:07.670
You can't afford

00:14:08.290 --> 00:14:09.550
Zhang Qishan's price.

00:14:09.700 --> 00:14:10.270
However,

00:14:11.000 --> 00:14:12.060
I can go easy on you.

00:14:13.700 --> 00:14:15.700
If you can take the wine from my hand,

00:14:16.100 --> 00:14:16.960
You win.

00:14:39.990 --> 00:14:41.700
You can't beat me like this!

00:14:42.290 --> 00:14:43.390
Do you know why?

00:14:43.500 --> 00:14:44.760
Because of believing.

00:14:45.130 --> 00:14:46.030
Believing

00:14:46.650 --> 00:14:48.030
Is the biggest trap.

00:14:50.050 --> 00:14:51.180
What do you believe?

00:14:52.240 --> 00:14:53.790
I believe that I am your dad.

00:14:55.870 --> 00:14:56.910
The guy outside—

00:14:58.050 --> 00:14:59.250
Do you believe in him?

00:15:01.290 --> 00:15:03.750
Although he usually seems a bit unreliable,

00:15:04.910 --> 00:15:06.030
I believe in him.

00:15:07.200 --> 00:15:08.460
Does he believe in you?

00:15:12.870 --> 00:15:14.800
You took such pains to lure me here.

00:15:14.870 --> 00:15:17.330
I assume it's not just to play Go and riddles.

00:15:18.430 --> 00:15:20.740
If Great Master Buddha wanted to drive us out of Changxiang,

00:15:20.740 --> 00:15:22.200
Why would he let you see me?

00:15:24.220 --> 00:15:26.000
What is Great Master Buddha's goal?

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:26.820
And you?

00:15:27.290 --> 00:15:28.410
What is your goal?

00:15:31.480 --> 00:15:32.980
To ask Great Master Buddha to help us

00:15:32.980 --> 00:15:34.030
Find Mo Yungao

00:15:34.060 --> 00:15:35.460
And rebuild the Archives.

00:15:35.460 --> 00:15:37.510
I'm not talking about your apparent goal.

00:15:37.510 --> 00:15:38.270
I mean...

00:15:39.220 --> 00:15:40.700
Your real goal.

00:15:46.010 --> 00:15:47.940
You have some special money on you,

00:15:47.970 --> 00:15:48.830
And there are

00:15:48.870 --> 00:15:50.420
Special marks on it.

00:15:50.860 --> 00:15:52.990
You drew them when you faked your death

00:15:53.800 --> 00:15:55.230
And left it for Zhang Hailou

00:15:55.230 --> 00:15:56.900
To investigate, right?

00:15:57.170 --> 00:15:58.640
The Nine Clans really lives up to its reputation.

00:15:58.640 --> 00:16:00.300
To deal with someone like you,

00:16:00.440 --> 00:16:01.820
I must be very careful

00:16:01.960 --> 00:16:03.620
And think through every step.

00:16:05.230 --> 00:16:06.580
Why do you say that?

00:16:09.340 --> 00:16:10.990
The Hidden Thread strategy

00:16:12.050 --> 00:16:14.110
Is not something just anyone can use.

00:16:17.700 --> 00:16:19.100
Hidden Thread strategy?

00:16:22.470 --> 00:16:23.370
Well then,

00:16:23.590 --> 00:16:25.230
Let me expose you.

00:16:26.790 --> 00:16:27.410
Suppose

00:16:28.170 --> 00:16:30.390
I want to set a trap for someone.

00:16:31.660 --> 00:16:33.710
If I lay everything out

00:16:33.730 --> 00:16:34.840
At once,

00:16:35.320 --> 00:16:36.650
It actually won't work.

00:16:37.700 --> 00:16:40.030
Because the target will easily become alert

00:16:40.030 --> 00:16:41.360
And realize it's a scam.

00:16:43.390 --> 00:16:45.480
But if, after setting the trap,

00:16:45.820 --> 00:16:46.620
I let them

00:16:46.620 --> 00:16:48.580
Find a very convincing clue

00:16:49.510 --> 00:16:51.350
And gradually

00:16:51.510 --> 00:16:53.320
Piece it together themselves,

00:16:53.450 --> 00:16:53.900
Then

00:16:54.270 --> 00:16:55.670
They will firmly believe

00:16:55.730 --> 00:16:57.890
That everything they figure out

00:16:58.150 --> 00:16:59.340
Is the truth

00:16:59.550 --> 00:17:00.410
And the answer.

00:17:01.270 --> 00:17:04.050
Then they will step right into the trap recklessly.

00:17:04.050 --> 00:17:05.609
Because no one doubts

00:17:05.660 --> 00:17:07.660
What they have deduced themselves.

00:17:07.740 --> 00:17:09.290
But the target won't know

00:17:09.660 --> 00:17:11.569
That all his reasoning processes,

00:17:11.569 --> 00:17:12.700
And even the ending,

00:17:13.640 --> 00:17:15.640
Are just part of the trap I designed.

00:17:16.609 --> 00:17:18.609
This is the Hidden Thread strategy.

00:17:19.900 --> 00:17:21.700
Everyone thought you were dead.

00:17:22.240 --> 00:17:23.980
So people would naturally think

00:17:23.980 --> 00:17:26.510
The clues you left are correct,

00:17:27.400 --> 00:17:28.930
Or at least not fabricated.

00:17:29.660 --> 00:17:30.610
But actually, they aren't.

00:17:30.610 --> 00:17:32.070
This is also a trap you set.

00:17:32.410 --> 00:17:33.810
Not only are you not dead,

00:17:34.090 --> 00:17:35.010
But you also used this method

00:17:35.010 --> 00:17:37.050
To deceive Salty Zhang and Zhang Haiqi.

00:17:37.050 --> 00:17:39.300
You pretend to be harmless,

00:17:39.440 --> 00:17:42.400
But in reality, you are the mastermind behind all this.

00:17:42.400 --> 00:17:43.050
You...

00:17:43.830 --> 00:17:45.620
Are Mo Yungao.

00:17:52.660 --> 00:17:54.480
[The Pure Charm of Bamboo]

00:18:13.350 --> 00:18:15.150
As expected of Ninth Master Xie.

00:18:15.290 --> 00:18:17.990
I imagined countless possibilities for our meeting,

00:18:17.990 --> 00:18:19.420
But I never expected you

00:18:20.070 --> 00:18:22.610
To give me such an astonishing deduction.

00:18:23.230 --> 00:18:25.430
However, it doesn't match the reality.

00:18:25.960 --> 00:18:27.180
I know who I am.

00:18:27.920 --> 00:18:28.980
I am not Mo Yungao.

00:18:31.110 --> 00:18:32.310
If I were,

00:18:32.310 --> 00:18:34.870
Why wouldn't I hide in the shadows and control everything?

00:18:34.870 --> 00:18:36.110
Why would I take the risk

00:18:36.110 --> 00:18:37.310
To fake my own death,

00:18:37.440 --> 00:18:38.900
And then come back to life?

00:18:39.400 --> 00:18:41.130
Wouldn't that be unnecessary?

00:18:43.900 --> 00:18:44.610
Unless

00:18:45.590 --> 00:18:46.920
I was already suspected

00:18:47.570 --> 00:18:49.770
And needed to use death to clear my name.

00:18:51.240 --> 00:18:52.640
But if that were the case,

00:18:53.270 --> 00:18:55.400
What reason would I have to resurrect?

00:18:56.110 --> 00:18:57.570
Coming back from the dead—

00:18:58.380 --> 00:19:00.310
Wouldn't it raise more suspicion?

00:19:02.180 --> 00:19:04.060
Great risks bring great rewards.

00:19:04.420 --> 00:19:06.000
What if by making this move,

00:19:06.070 --> 00:19:07.830
You could win the whole game?

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:11.750
Is there really no way in the world

00:19:11.750 --> 00:19:14.570
For Mo Yungao to disguise himself as Zhang Haixia?

00:19:18.810 --> 00:19:20.380
What if part of this scheme

00:19:20.590 --> 00:19:22.750
Is to deceive even yourself?

00:19:37.110 --> 00:19:38.230
Mo Yungao.

00:19:43.980 --> 00:19:45.600
What on earth are you up to?

00:19:47.530 --> 00:19:50.390
A confrontation between people is like playing Go.

00:19:50.410 --> 00:19:51.810
When you meet your match,

00:19:52.030 --> 00:19:53.530
You observe their moves.

00:19:53.840 --> 00:19:55.850
A person's heart can be seen through their moves.

00:19:55.850 --> 00:19:57.850
Only by understanding your opponent's mind

00:19:57.850 --> 00:19:58.940
Can you find

00:19:58.980 --> 00:20:00.550
A way to counter them

00:20:01.500 --> 00:20:02.570
And win the game.

00:20:17.500 --> 00:20:18.850
You mean...

00:20:19.250 --> 00:20:20.180
The question is,

00:20:20.680 --> 00:20:22.480
Can you win this game against me?

00:20:37.380 --> 00:20:38.000
Young man.

00:20:38.440 --> 00:20:39.480
Focus.

00:20:40.550 --> 00:20:42.210
If you can't pass this hurdle,

00:20:42.720 --> 00:20:43.640
You will

00:20:44.040 --> 00:20:46.170
Struggle with all the following ones.

00:21:23.500 --> 00:21:24.500
Are you giving up?

00:21:25.810 --> 00:21:27.070
I'm tired of fighting.

00:21:27.110 --> 00:21:28.170
I'm taking a break.

00:21:31.140 --> 00:21:33.880
They say Zhang Qishan is the Defense Commander of Changxiang

00:21:33.880 --> 00:21:35.460
And the head of the Old Nine Clans.

00:21:35.460 --> 00:21:36.610
You're so skilled.

00:21:36.640 --> 00:21:38.240
Are you one of the Nine Clans?

00:21:43.480 --> 00:21:44.320
We got to know each other through fighting.

00:21:44.320 --> 00:21:45.320
Let's be friends.

00:21:45.490 --> 00:21:46.780
I just want to know

00:21:47.270 --> 00:21:49.350
How you can let me pass.

00:21:50.770 --> 00:21:51.970
I don't need friends.

00:21:52.900 --> 00:21:54.230
And I can't let you pass.

00:21:56.850 --> 00:21:58.660
Is Zhang Qishan really that powerful?

00:21:58.660 --> 00:22:00.120
Are you that afraid of him?

00:22:02.230 --> 00:22:03.350
Entrusted by others,

00:22:03.350 --> 00:22:04.810
I cannot break my promise.

00:22:05.960 --> 00:22:06.770
How loyal.

00:22:07.050 --> 00:22:07.840
Young man,

00:22:08.070 --> 00:22:09.800
I have already told you earlier

00:22:09.880 --> 00:22:10.880
The way in and out.

00:22:11.900 --> 00:22:13.300
But you wouldn't listen.

00:22:14.030 --> 00:22:14.960
I asked,

00:22:16.000 --> 00:22:17.130
What do you believe?

00:22:18.680 --> 00:22:19.770
What do I believe?

00:22:23.090 --> 00:22:23.980
Believing

00:22:24.310 --> 00:22:25.550
Is the biggest trap.

00:22:26.830 --> 00:22:28.360
If you believe you are fast,

00:22:28.830 --> 00:22:30.560
Being fast is the biggest trap.

00:22:30.830 --> 00:22:32.630
And you will die from being fast.

00:22:32.680 --> 00:22:35.010
If you believe you are not afraid of death,

00:22:35.180 --> 00:22:37.110
Fearlessness is the biggest trap.

00:22:37.720 --> 00:22:39.400
And you will die from it.

00:22:40.330 --> 00:22:40.980
In short,

00:22:41.500 --> 00:22:42.770
Whatever you believe

00:22:43.400 --> 00:22:45.200
Is what will defeat you.

00:22:50.350 --> 00:22:50.980
Master.

00:22:53.270 --> 00:22:54.270
I understand now.

00:23:00.460 --> 00:23:01.060
By the way,

00:23:02.050 --> 00:23:03.310
What do you believe in?

00:23:04.030 --> 00:23:05.200
What do I believe in?

00:23:07.550 --> 00:23:10.350
You definitely believe this wine isn't poisoned.

00:23:14.150 --> 00:23:15.370
Didn't you drink it too?

00:23:15.370 --> 00:23:16.970
This bottle isn't poisoned.

00:23:18.100 --> 00:23:20.030
Don't worry. It's just a laxative.

00:23:20.420 --> 00:23:22.620
You'll be fine after you have diarrhea.

00:23:29.750 --> 00:23:31.330
Do you think using this little trick

00:23:31.330 --> 00:23:32.660
Would make me let you pass?

00:23:32.660 --> 00:23:34.180
Then do you think, when I fought you earlier,

00:23:34.180 --> 00:23:35.140
I gave it my all?

00:23:36.420 --> 00:23:36.960
Let me tell you,

00:23:36.960 --> 00:23:38.420
I'm from the Zhang family.

00:23:38.960 --> 00:23:40.980
I'm the same kind of person as Zhang Qishan.

00:23:40.980 --> 00:23:42.010
Didn't Zhang Qishan tell you

00:23:42.010 --> 00:23:43.470
That I'm his second uncle?

00:23:43.700 --> 00:23:44.720
I came to Changxiang this time

00:23:44.720 --> 00:23:46.000
To visit relatives.

00:23:46.110 --> 00:23:48.640
I didn't expect this junior to be so ignorant.

00:23:49.090 --> 00:23:52.150
It's time to emphasize the Zhang family's discipline.

00:23:53.330 --> 00:23:54.930
I'm going to get serious now.

00:24:00.090 --> 00:24:00.650
Come on!

00:24:30.980 --> 00:24:31.840
You bluffed me?

00:24:32.350 --> 00:24:33.420
You're right.

00:24:33.800 --> 00:24:35.530
Believing is the biggest trap.

00:24:36.140 --> 00:24:38.770
You believed your absolute strength was greater than mine,

00:24:38.770 --> 00:24:39.440
So when I made

00:24:39.440 --> 00:24:41.090
A move beyond your belief,

00:24:41.200 --> 00:24:42.310
You exposed a flaw.

00:24:42.840 --> 00:24:44.480
Even though it was just for a second,

00:24:44.480 --> 00:24:45.810
It was deadly enough.

00:24:49.960 --> 00:24:50.720
My mentor

00:24:51.360 --> 00:24:53.290
Demonstrated this move to me once,

00:24:54.350 --> 00:24:55.550
But I didn't learn it.

00:24:56.920 --> 00:24:57.900
That's not what I meant.

00:24:57.900 --> 00:24:59.830
The idea of believing I mentioned is actually a philosophy.

00:24:59.830 --> 00:25:00.890
I've learned a lot!

00:25:01.490 --> 00:25:02.490
I'll be going now!

00:25:04.530 --> 00:25:06.010
I'm Heibei of the Nine Clans,

00:25:06.010 --> 00:25:07.220
Sixth in rank!

00:25:07.640 --> 00:25:09.770
Let's have a drink together next time!

00:25:11.790 --> 00:25:12.460
Brat.

00:25:12.460 --> 00:25:13.990
This drug is really strong.

00:25:27.680 --> 00:25:29.110
Shrimpie, you scared me.

00:25:29.590 --> 00:25:30.450
So you're here.

00:25:33.140 --> 00:25:33.750
Shrimpie?

00:25:36.030 --> 00:25:36.630
Shrimpie?

00:25:44.610 --> 00:25:45.810
I'm not dead yet.

00:25:49.440 --> 00:25:50.420
Unbelievable.

00:25:51.350 --> 00:25:53.310
You're in the mood to play Go here?

00:25:51.580 --> 00:25:55.450
[The Pure Charm of Bamboo]

00:25:53.330 --> 00:25:54.660
I was fighting outside.

00:25:58.290 --> 00:26:01.020
I just ran into Ninth Master Xie of the Nine Clans.

00:26:01.830 --> 00:26:03.160
I just ran into

00:26:03.980 --> 00:26:04.740
Heibei, sixth in rank.

00:26:04.740 --> 00:26:06.400
-So what did he say to you? -So what did he say to you?

00:26:06.400 --> 00:26:07.830
He didn't say anything to me.

00:26:07.830 --> 00:26:08.850
We had a fight.

00:26:08.980 --> 00:26:10.290
But luckily I learned a move.

00:26:10.290 --> 00:26:11.290
So it was worth it.

00:26:12.220 --> 00:26:13.240
What about Ninth Master Xie?

00:26:13.240 --> 00:26:15.090
Don't tell me he was playing Go with you here.

00:26:15.090 --> 00:26:16.890
It was playing Go on the surface.

00:26:17.000 --> 00:26:18.880
He actually wanted to tell me something.

00:26:18.880 --> 00:26:19.680
Tell you what?

00:26:20.330 --> 00:26:22.130
Mo Yungao might not be Mo Yungao.

00:26:22.510 --> 00:26:23.770
I might be Mo Yungao.

00:26:24.790 --> 00:26:26.720
Mo Yungao might have replaced me.

00:26:28.160 --> 00:26:28.590
Wait.

00:26:29.500 --> 00:26:30.270
What?

00:26:30.670 --> 00:26:33.270
[The Pure Charm of Bamboo]

00:26:31.530 --> 00:26:33.130
Even though I might be Mo Yungao,

00:26:33.130 --> 00:26:35.140
We still have to stop him.

00:26:35.790 --> 00:26:36.420
Also,

00:26:37.750 --> 00:26:40.210
I discovered a possibility about Mo Yungao.

00:26:42.980 --> 00:26:45.780
Have you ever heard of the Hidden Thread strategy?

00:27:12.850 --> 00:27:13.830
So you're saying

00:27:13.830 --> 00:27:14.890
All of these things

00:27:14.920 --> 00:27:17.780
Are a Hidden Thread strategy designed by Mo Yungao?

00:27:19.090 --> 00:27:20.620
Me investigating the case,

00:27:20.790 --> 00:27:21.660
Destroying the Archives,

00:27:21.660 --> 00:27:22.500
And even saving you—

00:27:22.500 --> 00:27:24.140
They were all part of his plan?

00:27:24.140 --> 00:27:25.800
You are also a part of his trap?

00:27:27.750 --> 00:27:30.210
All the information we found out bit by bit

00:27:30.920 --> 00:27:32.980
Was likely planned by him in advance,

00:27:33.180 --> 00:27:34.740
Wanting us to find out.

00:27:35.790 --> 00:27:36.460
Perhaps

00:27:38.070 --> 00:27:39.310
His plan is to guide us

00:27:39.310 --> 00:27:40.610
In one direction,

00:27:41.300 --> 00:27:43.360
Where the situation is unknown to us.

00:27:45.050 --> 00:27:46.140
What is he up to?

00:27:51.290 --> 00:27:53.490
So I am reorganizing all the situations

00:27:54.330 --> 00:27:56.260
To list out all the possibilities.

00:27:59.270 --> 00:28:00.070
Wait a minute.

00:28:01.760 --> 00:28:03.150
If you are Mo Yungao,

00:28:03.850 --> 00:28:05.220
Why are you helping us

00:28:05.220 --> 00:28:07.090
Analyze Mo Yungao's situation?

00:28:09.090 --> 00:28:10.700
I might be Mo Yungao,

00:28:10.900 --> 00:28:11.740
But I might not be.

00:28:11.740 --> 00:28:13.070
So are you or aren't you?

00:28:18.290 --> 00:28:19.090
I don't know.

00:28:28.250 --> 00:28:29.580
The key to winning a game

00:28:30.030 --> 00:28:31.590
Is figuring out the opponent's moves

00:28:31.590 --> 00:28:33.320
And seeing through their mind.

00:28:33.610 --> 00:28:35.740
But if you can't figure out their mind,

00:28:36.110 --> 00:28:37.440
You must question everything

00:28:37.440 --> 00:28:38.840
You think is reasonable.

00:28:40.090 --> 00:28:42.350
Within those seemingly reasonable things,

00:28:42.350 --> 00:28:44.200
There must be hidden clues

00:28:45.250 --> 00:28:46.070
Regarding

00:28:46.590 --> 00:28:48.330
Mo Yungao's true intentions.

00:28:58.010 --> 00:28:58.790
I won.

00:29:04.370 --> 00:29:08.470
[The Pure Charm of Bamboo]

00:29:13.870 --> 00:29:16.000
What on earth does Mo Yungao want to do?

00:29:51.840 --> 00:29:54.210
If Ninth Master Xie was teaching me

00:29:54.790 --> 00:29:57.380
The Hidden Thread strategy as if I was Mo Yungao,

00:29:57.380 --> 00:29:59.240
Then whether I am Mo Yungao or not,

00:29:59.980 --> 00:30:01.310
I can use this strategy.

00:30:03.090 --> 00:30:04.010
But if Mo Yungao

00:30:04.010 --> 00:30:05.220
Has already used this strategy,

00:30:05.220 --> 00:30:07.280
Then everything we knew before

00:30:08.460 --> 00:30:10.860
Becomes even more unknown and terrifying.

00:30:15.210 --> 00:30:16.700
[The Pure Charm of Bamboo]

00:30:17.900 --> 00:30:19.960
Let's leave him with no moves to play.

00:30:21.180 --> 00:30:23.110
We'll go back to Xiacheng right now

00:30:23.660 --> 00:30:25.050
And live our lives happily.

00:30:25.050 --> 00:30:25.880
No matter what he does,

00:30:25.880 --> 00:30:27.080
Let's just ignore it.

00:30:27.250 --> 00:30:29.450
Do you think that would drive him crazy?

00:30:30.810 --> 00:30:32.570
When will you ever be reliable?

00:30:34.320 --> 00:30:35.350
But maybe

00:30:37.590 --> 00:30:39.120
It really could drive him crazy.

00:30:39.120 --> 00:30:39.730
Right?

00:30:48.530 --> 00:30:50.460
Mentor wants us to meet up with her.

00:30:54.440 --> 00:30:55.400
Who do you think

00:30:55.980 --> 00:30:57.830
Is more skilled, Great Master Buddha or Mentor?

00:30:57.830 --> 00:30:58.960
In the Zhang family,

00:30:59.200 --> 00:31:01.130
We don't belong to the same system.

00:31:02.070 --> 00:31:03.440
If we must compare them,

00:31:04.530 --> 00:31:06.860
You can say Mentor is Zhang Qishan's aunt.

00:31:08.850 --> 00:31:09.380
Alright.

00:31:09.980 --> 00:31:11.710
Then let's go meet this cousin.

00:31:14.030 --> 00:31:15.560
But since we're on his turf,

00:31:16.180 --> 00:31:18.440
We should at least show him some respect.

00:31:19.900 --> 00:31:21.500
What bad idea do you have now?

00:31:22.770 --> 00:31:23.300
Let's go.

00:31:32.980 --> 00:31:33.890
Great Master Buddha.

00:31:33.890 --> 00:31:35.920
Eighth Master is already at your residence.

00:31:35.920 --> 00:31:37.180
Sixth Master and Ninth Master

00:31:37.180 --> 00:31:38.420
Have engaged them.

00:31:38.620 --> 00:31:43.010
[Zhang Qishan, the First Clan of the Old Nine Clans]

00:31:40.140 --> 00:31:41.540
Don't be too optimistic.

00:31:42.240 --> 00:31:42.880
They...

00:31:43.770 --> 00:31:45.030
Are not easy to deal with.

00:31:45.030 --> 00:31:45.530
Yes.

00:31:59.240 --> 00:32:01.620
Great Master Buddha, previously, you gave me Changxiang tea.

00:32:01.620 --> 00:32:04.140
It goes perfectly with Xiacheng sweet fruit.

00:32:04.140 --> 00:32:05.940
This is a return gift. Please have a taste.

00:32:04.360 --> 00:32:06.110
[Qingjin Fruit]

00:32:07.300 --> 00:32:09.030
Mountains and seas do not meet.

00:32:09.530 --> 00:32:10.310
Miss Zhang,

00:32:10.770 --> 00:32:14.170
You should know the rules of the Zhang family better than I do.

00:32:23.530 --> 00:32:25.330
I'm here to talk about business.

00:32:25.660 --> 00:32:27.460
Please do me a favor, Great Master Buddha.

00:32:27.460 --> 00:32:28.640
If you get hurt,

00:32:29.680 --> 00:32:30.940
That wouldn't be good.

00:32:32.500 --> 00:32:33.230
If I get hurt,

00:32:33.660 --> 00:32:34.820
It's on me.

00:33:02.710 --> 00:33:04.350
Wu, let's go.

00:33:04.660 --> 00:33:05.160
Yes.

00:33:16.200 --> 00:33:18.010
Miss Zhang, you came from afar.

00:33:19.290 --> 00:33:21.590
I'd like to invite you to my residence for a chat.

00:33:21.590 --> 00:33:22.240
Alright.

00:33:22.550 --> 00:33:24.150
I will go find my people first

00:33:24.590 --> 00:33:25.520
And visit later.

00:33:30.760 --> 00:33:34.120
[Zhang Qishan's Residence]

00:33:40.310 --> 00:33:42.150
Guard the whole area within a one-kilometer radius

00:33:42.150 --> 00:33:43.200
Of Zhang's Residence.

00:33:43.200 --> 00:33:43.810
Yes!

00:33:44.260 --> 00:33:49.250
[Zhang's Residence]

00:33:44.390 --> 00:33:46.180
You two guard the entrance and exit.

00:33:46.180 --> 00:33:46.700
Yes!

00:33:54.980 --> 00:33:56.180
Listen up, everyone.

00:33:56.720 --> 00:33:59.110
Not even a fly is allowed to enter Zhang's Residence!

00:33:59.110 --> 00:33:59.970
Did you hear me?

00:34:00.180 --> 00:34:00.790
Yes!

00:34:07.440 --> 00:34:08.960
Do not disturb Great Master Buddha with this matter.

00:34:08.960 --> 00:34:09.300
Yes!

00:34:09.300 --> 00:34:09.610
Yes!

00:34:44.030 --> 00:34:44.670
Catch him!

00:34:44.840 --> 00:34:45.610
He is an imposter!

00:34:45.610 --> 00:34:46.260
Catch him!

00:35:03.480 --> 00:35:04.800
Take me to see my cousin.

00:35:04.800 --> 00:35:05.770
It's you?

00:35:06.130 --> 00:35:07.150
Or I'll kill you.

00:35:10.340 --> 00:35:10.940
Three!

00:35:13.920 --> 00:35:14.630
Two!

00:35:19.280 --> 00:35:20.390
Zhang Hailou.

00:35:24.590 --> 00:35:26.190
Did they give you a hard time?

00:35:27.420 --> 00:35:29.590
I have the situation under control.

00:35:30.090 --> 00:35:31.420
If anything happens...

00:35:34.710 --> 00:35:35.440
Adjutant.

00:35:35.460 --> 00:35:36.790
My people have arrived.

00:35:36.940 --> 00:35:38.390
Please inform Great Master Buddha

00:35:38.390 --> 00:35:40.450
And let us pay our respects together.

00:35:50.870 --> 00:35:52.260
Mentor, what did you do?

00:35:53.550 --> 00:35:55.010
I gave him a greeting gift.

00:35:56.920 --> 00:35:58.180
Where is Zhang Haixia?

00:35:58.980 --> 00:35:59.710
In case something happens,

00:35:59.710 --> 00:36:00.790
I had him wait outside.

00:36:00.790 --> 00:36:01.590
I'll call him.

00:36:18.500 --> 00:36:19.480
Where did this brat go?

00:36:19.480 --> 00:36:20.140
Never mind.

00:36:21.260 --> 00:36:22.780
Let's see Zhang Qishan first

00:36:22.780 --> 00:36:23.860
And meet up later.

00:36:25.730 --> 00:36:26.280
Mentor.

00:36:27.360 --> 00:36:28.560
Zhang Haixia is sick.

00:36:28.570 --> 00:36:30.170
After we return to Xiacheng,

00:36:30.260 --> 00:36:31.360
Can you treat him?

00:36:32.740 --> 00:36:33.340
Okay.

00:36:35.480 --> 00:36:37.940
You're not hiding anything from me, are you?

00:36:38.340 --> 00:36:39.300
You are so smart.

00:36:39.300 --> 00:36:41.300
What could I possibly hide from you?

00:36:41.630 --> 00:36:43.550
Stop thinking about Zhang Haixia.

00:36:43.550 --> 00:36:44.440
Right now,

00:36:44.920 --> 00:36:47.250
We must get Zhang Qishan's support first.

00:36:51.730 --> 00:36:53.070
Under the current circumstances,

00:36:53.070 --> 00:36:54.530
How do you describe our mindset

00:36:54.530 --> 00:36:55.500
In meeting Zhang Qishan?

00:36:55.500 --> 00:36:57.310
If we must describe it,

00:36:57.940 --> 00:36:59.110
It's like

00:36:59.420 --> 00:37:02.400
Poor country relatives visiting to claim ties.

00:37:04.150 --> 00:37:05.350
So we are claiming ties?

00:37:05.350 --> 00:37:06.010
No.

00:37:06.230 --> 00:37:07.000
You are.

00:37:10.800 --> 00:37:11.460
Miss Zhang.

00:37:12.130 --> 00:37:12.860
You may go in.

00:37:46.440 --> 00:37:48.700
When exactly did you come to Changxiang?

00:37:56.210 --> 00:37:58.120
That person was no juggler.

00:38:37.640 --> 00:38:45.880
[No. 5, Shatong Road]

00:38:48.260 --> 00:38:48.880
Who is it?

00:38:54.060 --> 00:38:55.450
[No. 5, Shatong Road]

00:39:01.560 --> 00:39:05.460
[No. 5, Shatong Road]

00:39:10.890 --> 00:39:11.800
Ninth Master.

00:39:13.010 --> 00:39:14.380
Great Master Buddha took so much trouble

00:39:14.380 --> 00:39:16.110
To get the Nine Clans involved.

00:39:18.010 --> 00:39:19.450
Is it actually a test

00:39:19.470 --> 00:39:20.930
For us?

00:39:26.550 --> 00:39:28.700
It seems Great Master Buddha wants to see us.

00:39:28.700 --> 00:39:30.130
Since he wants to see us,

00:39:30.680 --> 00:39:31.920
He will help.

00:39:32.960 --> 00:39:34.420
It's just inconvenient for him to do so because of his status.

00:39:34.420 --> 00:39:35.810
You've said it all,

00:39:36.500 --> 00:39:38.100
So I have nothing left to say.

00:39:38.650 --> 00:39:39.430
Then,

00:39:40.480 --> 00:39:42.140
Does Great Master Buddha have

00:39:42.280 --> 00:39:43.940
Further instructions for us?

00:39:44.360 --> 00:39:45.190
If he does,

00:39:45.480 --> 00:39:46.280
You'll know.

00:39:51.820 --> 00:40:00.540
[No. 5, Shatong Road]

00:39:57.770 --> 00:39:59.400
Looks like the person Great Master Buddha

00:39:59.400 --> 00:40:00.650
Told us to wait for is you,

00:40:00.650 --> 00:40:01.950
Mr. Zhang Haixia.

00:40:02.710 --> 00:40:04.360
We are the suicide warriors of the Zhang family.

00:40:04.360 --> 00:40:05.550
The upcoming mission

00:40:05.550 --> 00:40:06.510
Is very dangerous.

00:40:06.510 --> 00:40:08.190
We might not be able to make it back.

00:40:08.190 --> 00:40:09.570
If you want to quit—

00:40:09.710 --> 00:40:10.560
Great Master Buddha has said

00:40:10.560 --> 00:40:12.150
That he wouldn't force you.

00:40:14.150 --> 00:40:15.280
I've made up my mind.

00:40:16.550 --> 00:40:17.190
Mr. Zhang.

00:40:17.780 --> 00:40:19.180
Great Master Buddha said

00:40:19.190 --> 00:40:20.460
You will be in command

00:40:20.550 --> 00:40:21.950
Of the upcoming mission.

00:40:22.480 --> 00:40:24.650
Then we need to set off as soon as possible.

00:40:24.650 --> 00:40:25.710
Where are we going?

00:40:25.920 --> 00:40:26.710
The Xiao River.

